name: iter::traits::iterator::Iterator::gt

cmp::PartialEq::eq.doc: Tests for `self` and `other` values to be equal, and is used by `==`.

src:
fn gt<I>(self, other: I) -> bool
    where
        I: IntoIterator,
        Self::Item: PartialOrd<I::Item>,
        Self: Sized,
    {
        self.partial_cmp(other) == Some(Ordering::Greater)
    }
